data.description: Welcome to your new home, where comfort and versatility meet in perfect harmony! This spacious 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and style, including a flexible upstairs room that can adapt to your lifestyle.  Upon entering, your first impression is a charming sitting area that beckons you to relax and unwind. This flows seamlessly into the living area, creating an ideal space for entertaining family and friends.   The main floor also houses a guest bedroom with a nearby full bathroom, perfect for accommodating guests or using as a home office. You'll appreciate the convenience of a separate laundry room and access to the attached two-car garage.  Upstairs, you'll discover a spacious primary suite that includes a walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom with dual vanities, a soaking tub, and a separate shower. Two additional well-proportioned bedrooms share a third full bathroom, ensuring that everyone has their own space and privacy.  The highlight of the second floor is the versatile flex room. Whether you need a home gym, a playroom, a media center, or a cozy retreat to unwind, this space can be tailored to your unique needs.  Outside, the backyard offers plenty of room for outdoor activities, gardening, or relaxing on the patio. It's the perfect canvas for creating your outdoor oasis.  Nearby, you'll find top-rated schools, parks, shopping centers, and easy access to major commuting routes.Don't miss the opportunity to make this spacious and versatile residence your forever home. Schedule a showing today and explore all the possibilities it has to offer!
